languages.text: "Когда вернемся на Футфол, напомни мне, о венценосная и бледноликая, сводить тебя на один очень "домашний" концерт. С кулуарными танцами и душистыми винами".
"When we are back on Footfall, remind me, my crown-bearing and pallid-featured beauty, to take you to a 'concert' of sorts at a certain 'parlour.' With private dances and heady wines."

languages.text: « Une fois de retour à Castel, ma beauté couronnée au teint d'albâtre, rappelez-moi de vous inviter à un "concert" très spécial dans mon "salon" préféré. Je vous promets des danses privées et du vin à volonté. »
languages.original_text: "When we are back on Footfall, remind me, my crown-bearing and pallid-featured beauty, to take you to a 'concert' of sorts at a certain 'parlour.' With private dances and heady wines."

languages.text: “等咱们回到落脚港之后，记得提醒我，我要和这位头戴皇冠、面色苍白的美人儿一起去某个‘厅堂’里听场‘音乐会’，到时候还会有私人舞蹈和美酒呢。”

languages.text: «Cuando volvamos a Paso, recuérdeme, mi belleza con corona y rasgos pálidos, que {mf|le|la} lleve a un "concierto" en cierta "cámara". Con bailes privados y vinos embriagadores».
languages.original_text: "When we are back on Footfall, remind me, my crown-bearing and pallid-featured beauty, to take you to a 'concert' of sorts at a certain 'parlour.' With private dances and heady wines."

languages.text: "Wenn wir wieder auf Footfall sind, erinnert mich daran, meine kronentragende und bleichgesichtige Schönheit, Euch zu einem 'Konzert' in einem gewissen 'Salon' einzuladen. Mit Privattanz und süßem Wein."

languages.text: "Benim solgun tenli, taçlı güzelim; Binliman'a döndüğümüzde hatırlat da seni malum 'salondaki' bir 'konsere' götüreyim. Özel danslar ve mest eden şaraplar da cabası."

traits.locale_text: "Taçlı, açık tenli afet hanım; Binliman'a döndüğümüzde hatırlat da seni malum 'salondaki' bir 'konsere' götüreyim. Özel danslar ve sert şaraplar da cabası."
